episodes.title: The Cult That Promised A Beautiful Ending
episodes.description:
This recording documents the rise and collapse of a closed spiritual organization active in Europe and Canada during the late twentieth century. Order of The Solar Temple, was a new religious movement and secret society, often described as a cult, notorious for the mass deaths of many of its members in several mass murders and suicides throughout the 1990s.

The videos are designed to be listened to, using calm narration and minimal visuals. Content is drawn from documented history, reported accounts, archived testimonies, reconstructed records and folklore.
